  <heading>SCVTF</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>Multi-vector signed integer convert to floating-point</brief>
    <description>
      <para>Convert to single-precision from signed 32-bit integer, each element of the two or four source vectors, and place the results in the corresponding elements of the two or four destination vectors.</para>
      <para>This instruction follows SME2 floating-point numerical behaviors corresponding to instructions that place their results in one or more SVE Z vectors.</para>
      <para>This instruction is unpredicated.</para>
    </description>
    <status>Green</status>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
    <sm_policy>SM_1_only</sm_policy>
  </desc>
